h1. Description

This bundle provides JMX MBeans related to the Karaf system service.

In particular, a SystemMBean is provided that can be remotely administered using a JMX client (for instance
JConsole).

With this SystemMBean, you have the following operations available:
* shutdown() - Shutdown the Karaf container.
* shutdown(time) - Shutdown the Karaf container as a given time.
* setStartLevel(startLevel) - Set the Karaf system start level.
* getStartLevel() - Get the Karaf system start level.

